S.FORM: Alexander Van der Bellen u siwkay niza tatama, 1 bulad 18 demiad, Alexander Van der Bellen, u misingkiway. 1944 a mihca nalecuhan) u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Austria ayza sa ci Alexander Van der Bellen, micakat a demiad sa i 2017 a mihca 1 bulad 26 demiad. naku sasaydang ciniza, pasubana' i tabakiay a cacudadan. mikinkiw ciniza ku kyizay. 2016.12.4 maala ciniza ku Cungtung singkiw, mamikuwan tu ku Cungtung ni Awtili kanatal. u ngangan niza u sulit nu Hulam: u sulit nu : Alexander Van der Bellen kakuniza u nasulitan nu Hulam atu Amilika . . 2016 12 4 51.7 ( 48.3 ) . Alexander Van der Bellen is an Austrianpolitician and economist who is the 12th and current State President of Austria since 26 January 2017. malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government Awtili misingkiw tu Cungtung, sakawananay macakat masetul tu Aouco Alexander Van der Bellen maala ku Cungtung nu Awtili
